Here we can use to monitor and logging the server 

In kuberenetes we have  heapstar tool is used to monitor in starting now but it can be used the  ***Metrics server*** 

In the way of the metric server firstly we need to install the metrics by this way 

 

Minikube addons enable metric server 

 

Kubectl top node   #used to view the monnitoring of the nodes 

Kubectl  top pod  

 

Kubectl logs nameof the pod 

 
